        "author_association": "MEMBER",
        "body": ">I want to be able to tell users to use the top level API and use map_partitions as an escape hatch\r\n\r\nI personally view `map_partitions` as both and \"escape hatch\" and an optimization. I agree that we should treat pathological cases like this seriously, but I have a feeling we may have better luck encouraging the use of `map_partitions` when the user/dev **knows** munual fusion makes the most sense .",
